  <walkingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Opatija, situated at the foot of mighty Mt Ucka (1,400m) and its National Park, offers wonderful walking opportunities. There are a variety of marked trails through the national park with dotted waterfalls. The 12km Lungomare, between fishing village of Volosko to Lovran, offers an enjoyable walk with beautiful scenery. Many traditional mountain villages around Opatija offer wonderful views towards the Kvarner Bay.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>]]></walkingDescription>
